The paper deals with object detection and classification using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs), which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves region proposal, which is a technique used in machine learning and computer vision (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the speed and efficiency of the proposed method, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
